莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）谈论“接受痛苦”和大卫港（David Harbour）分裂之后的潜在新纹身https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-ally-allen-talks-ceppering-pain-and-and-pain-and-potential-new-tattoo-dattoo-after-david-harbour-split-split-split-3839151？艾伦说话 - 戴上纹身及david-harbour-splitAnagricel Duran Tue, 18 Feb 2025 19:48:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3839151 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在2025年春季时装秀的Giorgio Armani RTW。 （John Nacion/WWD的照片通过Getty Images）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你必须坐在痛苦中，面对痛苦，接受痛苦”</p><p>莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在大卫港（David Harbour）拆分后首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-talks-accepting-pain-and-potential-new-tattoo-after-david-harbour-split-3839151">“接受痛苦”和潜在的新纹身</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）在2025年春季时装秀的Giorgio Armani RTW。 （John Nacion/WWD的照片通过Getty Images）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Lily-Allen-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Lily-Allen">莉莉·艾伦（Lily Allen）</a>公开了她的“接受痛苦”的旅程，以及在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-harbour">戴维·港（David Harbour）</a>分裂后，她有可能获得纹身以纪念纹身。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-and-david-harbour-have-reportedly-separated-after-four-years-of-marriage-3834929">本月初报道了这对夫妇分居四年后分居</a>的消息。艾伦（Allen）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><em>陌生人事物（</em></a> Allen and Stranger）在约会应用程序会议上开会后，演员港开始约会，并于2020年9月在拉斯维加斯亲密的拉斯维加斯仪式上结婚。</p><p>艾伦（Allen）最近透露，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-speaks-out-on-time-in-treatment-centre-for-emotional-turmoil-after-david-harbour-split-3838153">进入了一个治疗中心，以应对溢出后的“情感动荡”</a> 。</p><p>现在，与联合主持人Miquita Oliver在二人组的最新<em>想念中对话？</em>播客剧集“微笑”的杀手表达了她对获得新纹身的兴趣，该纹身突出了“接受痛苦”的信息。灵感来自她的最新读物，该书是关于“自我同情”的。</p><p>她告诉奥利弗（Oliver）说：“这对我来说真的很突出，我什至可以把它当作纹身，它&#39;遭受X痛=抵抗力&#39;。”她继续说：“您必须坐在痛苦中，面对痛苦并接受痛苦。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGLFoXbtEMo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=